Philips SICP Python Client

This project is an independent Python client for the Philips Serial / Ethernet
Interface Communication Protocol (SICP). It is not affiliated with, endorsed by,
or sponsored by Philips, TPV, or PPDS.

Philips and related product names are trademarks or registered trademarks of
their respective owners. They are used in this project only to identify display
models and protocol compatibility.

The implementation and project documentation are based on observed behavior,
publicly available information, and development notes from SICP protocol
materials. The protocol reference in docs/ is retained as development
documentation for interoperability.
